imdb.plot outline: Nothing to add is a documentary series on Degrowth based on a sociological approach. It is a space of free expression, a citizen forum offered to non-specialists from French society. The participants unfold their thoughts without adding anything, without their word being distorted or interrupted. A political space in the noble sense of the word that takes the party to trust the spectators; its analytical capacity and critical mind.
imdb.title: Nothing to Add La Décroissance
